# 3. Course Objectives

1. Understand cybersecurity principles and AI concepts.
2. Apply machine learning algorithms for cyber threat detection.
3. Develop deep learning models for malware detection and intrusion detection.
4. Analyse AI-enabled cybersecurity solutions.
5. Evaluate ethical, explainable, and responsible AI practices.
6. Design intelligent cybersecurity applications using real-world datasets.

